	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Apr 2nd 7:25 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hail to all!&nbsp;&nbsp;I am recruiting for a guild that's going to start in June on the Karana server.  It will be open to all classes and race.  The charter and reason as to what purpose this guild serves is being formulated as we speak.  You will not be able to find me on the game, for I am currently deployed.  The founders of this guild are all newbies to the game all below lvl 20, but some might be higher when the guild timeframe comes around.  Post a reply and look for more messages pertaining to the subject.  I suggest looking for Viego in Queynos for more information.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
