	   <tr><td colspan=2>I use the hotbox and instead of just having songs there, I have items from my 2-3 Inventory slots and my primary and secondary in there. So out of 10 hotbox slots, i would use maybe 5 - 6 for songs, and the rest equipments. And each different hotbox, I would have different setup depending on if I solo, or group. Then i would just basically switch from there while i twist my songs. <br><br>Just be careful when trying to put the slots from the inv. and weapons into your Hotbox, you kinda have to allign the top left with the middle of the hotbox slot instead of tyring to align the upper left with upper left.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you use upper left and upper left, you will see that it does not work and get frustrated like me at first :-). <br><br>Hope it helps :-)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
